=== Cultural properties ===
; Chofu City designated tangible cultural properties
* Honden (designated March 30, 2012)
: Built in 1683; repaired in 1815. One-bay nagare-zukuri mise-dana style. Original thatched roof replaced with copper sheeting.<ref name="cityprop">Chofu City Board of Education signboard for Kohaku Shrine Honden and three munafuda.</ref>
* Three munafuda attached to the honden (designated March 30, 2012)
: Include inscriptions from 750, 1683, and 1815.<ref name="cityprop"/>

; Other items
* Stone torii (built 1828)
* Monument "Komae-go Sasu-mura Kohaku Jinja no Hi"
* Komainu (built 1908)
* Haiden

